name: Hungry Hawk
overview: You are a hawk named Harry Hawk trying to catch hopping rabbits,but watch out for hot air balloons, vicious eagles and the electric fence! All Harry Hawk wants to do is catch rabbits, but his is not an easy life. In the sky killer eagles and balloons make flying hazardous. In the grass below is a hidden electric fence. Also if he misses 5 rabbits in a row, he will starve.
